{"abstract":[{"text":"Provider of spaces semantic tokens to use for alert spaces","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spaces"},{"text":": any ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract30AllSpaceSemanticTokensProviderP","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider\/spaces","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B33ThemeAlertComponentTokensProviderC6spaces0A8Contract016AllSpaceSemanticfG0_pvp","symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Property","title":"spaces","fragments":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"spaces","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": any ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract30AllSpaceSemanticTokensProviderP"}]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider\/spaces"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"references":{"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of alert"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"alert"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSAlert"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllAlertComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AlertComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"alert"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Alert"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of borders ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBorderSemanticTokensProviders"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":") and sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"}],"type":"topic","title":"OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider"},"ic_theme_orange.png":{"type":"image","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/documentation/OUDSThemesContract/AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"TokensProvider","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract14TokensProviderP"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SpaceMultipleSemanticTokens","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic013SpaceMultipleB6TokensP"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"SpaceSemanticTokens","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic05SpaceB6TokensP"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Something which provides all semantic tokens of space"}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemescontract\/allspacesemantictokensprovider","title":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider/spaces":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeAlertComponentTokensProvider\/spaces","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemealertcomponenttokensprovider\/spaces","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Provider of spaces semantic tokens to use for alert spaces"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"spaces"},{"kind":"text","text":": any "},{"text":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSThemesContract30AllSpaceSemanticTokensProviderP"}],"type":"topic","title":"spaces"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","title":"Theme Orange","role":"collection","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic "},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example."}],"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"}}}